---
import RootLayout from '../../layouts/RootLayout.astro';
---

<RootLayout
	title="Photo, Video & Drone Services in Lexington, KY - NOZA LLC"
	description="Professional photography, videography, and drone services for realtors, contractors, and businesses in Lexington Kentucky. Cinematic content that sells."
	lang="en"
	alternateUrl="/es/photo-video"
>
	<!-- Hero Section -->
	<section class="video-hero">
		<div class="cosmic-background">
			<div class="stars"></div>
			<div class="nebula nebula-1"></div>
			<div class="nebula nebula-2"></div>
			<div class="nebula nebula-3"></div>
		</div>

		<div class="particles"></div>

		<div class="hero-content">
			<h1 class="video-headline">Photo, Video & Drone Services in Lexington, KY</h1>
			<p class="video-subheadline">Cinematic visual content that captures attention and sells. From property showcases to product cinematography, we create stunning media that tells your story.</p>
			<div class="hero-pricing">
				<a href="/contact" class="price-badge">Free Discovery Call</a>
				<span class="price-subtext">Professional photo or video shoots</span>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Media Intro Section -->
	<section class="media-intro">
		<div class="intro-container">
			<h2 class="intro-title">Visual Storytelling That Converts</h2>
			<p class="intro-text">
				In today's visual-first world, quality photos and videos aren't luxury‚Äîthey're necessity. Whether you're selling a property, showcasing your business, or launching a product, professional visual content builds trust, engages viewers, and drives sales.
			</p>
			<p class="intro-text">
				Our team combines technical expertise with creative vision. We don't just capture images; we craft cinematic experiences that resonate with your audience. From drone aerial perspectives to intimate product shots, we bring your vision to life with stunning clarity and emotion.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Services Section -->
	<section class="media-services">
		<div class="services-container">
			<h2 class="services-title">Our Media Services</h2>
			
			<div class="services-grid">
				<div class="service-card-item">
					<div class="service-card-icon photo-icon"></div>
					<h3>Professional Photography</h3>
					<p>High-quality still photography for real estate, products, events, portraits, and more. Each image is carefully composed and edited for maximum impact.</p>
					<ul class="service-features">
						<li>Real estate photography</li>
						<li>Product photography</li>
						<li>Event coverage</li>
						<li>Portrait sessions</li>
						<li>Professional retouching</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div class="service-card-item">
					<div class="service-card-icon video-icon"></div>
					<h3>Cinematic Videography</h3>
					<p>Broadcast-quality video production that tells your story. From real estate tours to testimonials to branded content, we create videos that engage and convert.</p>
					<ul class="service-features">
						<li>Real estate property videos</li>
						<li>Business testimonials</li>
						<li>Product showcase videos</li>
						<li>Event coverage</li>
						<li>Brand storytelling</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div class="service-card-item">
					<div class="service-card-icon drone-icon"></div>
					<h3>Drone Aerial Photography</h3>
					<p>Licensed drone pilots capturing breathtaking aerial perspectives. Perfect for property listings, construction progress, real estate marketing, and landscape showcases.</p>
					<ul class="service-features">
						<li>Aerial property photography</li>
						<li>Real estate flyovers</li>
						<li>Construction project tracking</li>
						<li>Landscape & terrain shots</li>
						<li>Licensed & insured</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div class="service-card-item">
					<div class="service-card-icon edit-icon"></div>
					<h3>Professional Editing & Post-Production</h3>
					<p>Color grading, editing, motion graphics, and effects that elevate your footage. We enhance what we capture to create polished, professional final products.</p>
					<ul class="service-features">
						<li>Professional color grading</li>
						<li>Video editing & sound design</li>
						<li>Motion graphics</li>
						<li>Thumbnails & graphics</li>
						<li>Fast turnaround</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div class="service-card-item">
					<div class="service-card-icon livestream-icon"></div>
					<h3>Live Streaming & Virtual Tours</h3>
					<p>Live stream events, open houses, or product launches. Virtual tours let remote buyers explore properties from anywhere. Professional setup and execution.</p>
					<ul class="service-features">
						<li>Live event streaming</li>
						<li>Property virtual tours</li>
						<li>Multi-camera setups</li>
						<li>Professional audio</li>
						<li>Interactive features</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div class="service-card-item">
					<div class="service-card-icon package-icon"></div>
					<h3>Complete Media Packages</h3>
					<p>Integrated photo and video packages that cover all your visual needs. Drone photography, cinematic video, professional photography, and editing all working together.</p>
					<ul class="service-features">
						<li>Custom tailored packages</li>
						<li>Bundled services</li>
						<li>Flexible scheduling</li>
						<li>Fast delivery</li>
						<li>Licensing included</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Who Benefits Section -->
	<section class="who-benefits-video">
		<div class="benefits-container">
			<h2 class="benefits-title">Who We Create Media For</h2>
			
			<div class="benefits-grid">
				<div class="benefit-card">
					<div class="benefit-icon realtors"></div>
					<h3>Real Estate Agents & Brokers</h3>
					<p>Professional photography and drone footage help properties sell faster and for more money. Virtual tours let buyers explore 24/7. We help you close more deals.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="benefit-card">
					<div class="benefit-icon contractors"></div>
					<h3>Contractors & Builders</h3>
					<p>Showcase your work with stunning before/after photography and project progression videos. Build portfolio material that lands new clients and impressive bids.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="benefit-card">
					<div class="benefit-icon businesses"></div>
					<h3>Small Businesses & Shops</h3>
					<p>Product photography, business photography, and promotional videos that showcase your business professionally. Stand out on social media and your website.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="benefit-card">
					<div class="benefit-icon hospitality"></div>
					<h3>Hotels, Restaurants & Venues</h3>
					<p>Beautiful imagery that attracts guests. Professional photos of spaces, amenities, and food increase bookings and positive reviews online.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="benefit-card">
					<div class="benefit-icon events"></div>
					<h3>Event Planners & Venues</h3>
					<p>Capture the magic of events. Professional coverage creates portfolio material and helps market future events. Live streaming brings remote attendance.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="benefit-card">
					<div class="benefit-icon ecommerce"></div>
					<h3>E-commerce & Online Brands</h3>
					<p>Product photography that sells. Professional images and video demonstrations increase conversion rates and reduce returns. Lifestyle shots that tell your brand story.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Video Impact Section -->
	<section class="video-impact">
		<div class="impact-container">
			<h2 class="impact-title">The Power of Visual Content</h2>
			
			<div class="impact-grid">
				<div class="impact-item">
					<div class="impact-number">80%</div>
					<p>of consumers say video makes them more likely to buy</p>
				</div>

				<div class="impact-item">
					<div class="impact-number">2.6X</div>
					<p>more engagement with video posts on social media</p>
				</div>

				<div class="impact-item">
					<div class="impact-number">93%</div>
					<p>of property listings with photos get more inquiries</p>
				</div>

				<div class="impact-item">
					<div class="impact-number">90%</div>
					<p>of shoppers consider product videos important</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Production Process Section -->
	<section class="production-process">
		<div class="process-container">
			<h2 class="process-title">Our Production Process</h2>
			<p class="process-subtitle">From concept to final delivery</p>

			<div class="process-steps">
				<div class="process-step">
					<div class="step-number">01</div>
					<div class="step-content">
						<h3>Discovery & Planning</h3>
						<p>We discuss your vision, goals, and timeline. What story are we telling? What's the intended use? We plan shots, angles, and production schedule.</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="process-connector"></div>

				<div class="process-step">
					<div class="step-number">02</div>
					<div class="step-content">
						<h3>Production Day</h3>
						<p>We arrive with professional equipment and expertise. Professional-grade cameras, lighting, drones, and audio capture stunning media. We direct and compose every shot.</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="process-connector"></div>

				<div class="process-step">
					<div class="step-number">03</div>
					<div class="step-content">
						<h3>Post-Production & Editing</h3>
						<p>We edit, color grade, add effects, and polish every frame. Professional sound design ensures audio is pristine. Every detail is refined for maximum impact.</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="process-connector"></div>

				<div class="process-step">
					<div class="step-number">04</div>
					<div class="step-content">
						<h3>Review & Revisions</h3>
						<p>You review the final product. We make revisions to ensure you're thrilled with the result. Your approval is essential before final delivery.</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="process-connector"></div>

				<div class="process-step">
					<div class="step-number">05</div>
					<div class="step-content">
						<h3>Final Delivery & Licensing</h3>
						<p>You receive final files in all necessary formats. High-resolution stills, video files, web-optimized versions. Full usage rights and licensing documentation included.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Media Uses Section -->
	<section class="media-uses">
		<div class="uses-container">
			<h2 class="uses-title">How to Use Your Media</h2>
			<p class="uses-subtitle">Professional content works across all your channels</p>

			<div class="uses-grid">
				<div class="use-item">
					<div class="use-visual website-use"></div>
					<h3>Website Showcase</h3>
					<p>High-quality images and video enhance your website, build trust, and improve SEO. Background videos, product galleries, and hero images matter.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="use-item">
					<div class="use-visual social-use"></div>
					<h3>Social Media</h3>
					<p>Photos and videos perform best on social platforms. Share progress, behind-scenes, results, and testimonials. Visual content drives engagement and followers.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="use-item">
					<div class="use-visual marketing-use"></div>
					<h3>Marketing Materials</h3>
					<p>Brochures, presentations, ads, emails‚Äîprofessional images and video elevate all marketing. Consistent visual identity across every touchpoint.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="use-item">
					<div class="use-visual listings-use"></div>
					<h3>Real Estate Listings</h3>
					<p>Photos and video tours increase interest and showings. Drone footage showcases properties from unique perspectives. Virtual tours sell properties faster.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="use-item">
					<div class="use-visual advertising-use"></div>
					<h3>Paid Advertising</h3>
					<p>Video ads get 1200% more shares than text and images combined. Professional video dramatically improves ad performance and ROI.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="use-item">
					<div class="use-visual portfolio-use"></div>
					<h3>Portfolio & Case Studies</h3>
					<p>Build your portfolio with before/after photos and project videos. Showcase your best work to attract premium clients and higher rates.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Photo & Video FAQ Section -->
	<section class="media-faq">
		<div class="faq-header">
			<h2 class="faq-title">Photo & Video Questions Answered</h2>
			<p class="faq-subtitle">Everything you need to know about professional media services</p>
		</div>

		<div class="faq-container">
			<details class="faq-item">
				<summary class="faq-question">How much does professional photography cost?</summary>
				<div class="faq-answer">
					<p>Professional photography starts at $400 for a 2-4 hour shoot, including professional editing. Real estate property photography typically runs $500-$1,500 depending on property size. Product photography and event coverage vary. We offer custom packages matching your budget and needs.</p>
				</div>
			</details>

			<details class="faq-item">
				<summary class="faq-question">What about drone photography? Do you have proper licensing?</summary>
				<div class="faq-answer">
					<p>Yes! Our drone pilots are FAA Part 107 licensed and fully insured. We follow all regulations for commercial drone operations. Drone photography adds unique aerial perspectives perfect for real estate, construction, and property showcases. Pricing starts at $500 for drone shoots.</p>
				</div>
			</details>

			<details class="faq-item">
				<summary class="faq-question">Can you do video for real estate listings?</summary>
				<div class="faq-answer">
					<p>Absolutely. We create property walkthrough videos, cinematic property tours, and virtual tours that showcase homes beautifully. Video listings get significantly more engagement and inquiries. We combine photography, videography, and drone footage for complete property showcases.</p>
				</div>
			</details>

			<details class="faq-item">
				<summary class="faq-question">How long does production take?</summary>
				<div class="faq-answer">
					<p>Shoot day can range from 2-8 hours depending on scope. Post-production typically takes 1-2 weeks depending on volume and complexity. We prioritize fast turnaround while maintaining quality. Rush delivery is available for urgent projects.</p>
				</div>
			</details>

			<details class="faq-item">
				<summary class="faq-question">What if there's bad weather for outdoor shoots?</summary>
				<div class="faq-answer">
					<p>We can reschedule outdoor shoots for better weather or adapt. Some shoots work great in different lighting. Drone flights require clear weather and good visibility‚Äîwe'll reschedule if conditions aren't safe. For time-sensitive projects, we discuss contingency plans upfront.</p>
				</div>
			</details>

			<details class="faq-item">
				<summary class="faq-question">Do you provide all the edited files and final media?</summary>
				<div class="faq-answer">
					<p>Yes. You receive all final files in multiple formats: high-resolution stills, web-optimized images, video files in multiple resolutions, and any graphics or thumbnails created. You own the media and have full rights to use it however you want.</p>
				</div>
			</details>

			<details class="faq-item">
				<summary class="faq-question">Can you do video editing or just production?</summary>
				<div class="faq-answer">
					<p>We handle the complete process: production, filming, and professional post-production editing. We edit, color grade, add music, graphics, and effects. We can work from raw footage you provide or shoot everything ourselves.</p>
				</div>
			</details>

			<details class="faq-item">
				<summary class="faq-question">Do you offer virtual tours or 360 photography?</summary>
				<div class="faq-answer">
					<p>Yes! We create interactive virtual tours perfect for real estate and venue showcases. 360 photography gives viewers the ability to explore properties from anywhere. Matterport and similar platforms integrate seamlessly with websites and listing sites.</p>
				</div>
			</details>

			<details class="faq-item">
				<summary class="faq-question">What's the turnaround time for final delivery?</summary>
				<div class="faq-answer">
					<p>Standard delivery is 1-2 weeks from shoot date. We can offer expedited turnaround (3-5 days) for an additional fee. For time-sensitive projects, we discuss timeline upfront to ensure we can meet your needs.</p>
				</div>
			</details>

			<details class="faq-item">
				<summary class="faq-question">Do you service Lexington and Central Kentucky?</summary>
				<div class="faq-answer">
					<p>Yes! We're based in Lexington and specialize in serving local businesses, real estate agents, contractors, and venues throughout Central Kentucky. We also travel for larger projects. Contact us to discuss your specific needs.</p>
				</div>
			</details>

			<details class="faq-item">
				<summary class="faq-question">Can you combine media with my website or marketing?</summary>
				<div class="faq-answer">
					<p>Perfect! We integrate professional photos and videos into website builds, marketing campaigns, social media, and advertising. Your visual content is most powerful when it's part of a complete marketing strategy. We work closely with our web and marketing teams.</p>
				</div>
			</details>

			<details class="faq-item">
				<summary class="faq-question">Do you offer rush service or same-day delivery?</summary>
				<div class="faq-answer">
					<p>For urgent projects, we can prioritize post-production. Same-day delivery of select images is possible. Rush service fees apply depending on timeline. Contact us to discuss your deadline and we'll do our best to accommodate.</p>
				</div>
			</details>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Media CTA Section -->
	<section class="media-cta">
		<div class="cta-content">
			<h2 class="cta-title">Ready to Capture Your Best Visual Story?</h2>
			<p class="cta-description">Let's create stunning photos and videos that showcase your business, property, or product. Professional media that gets results.</p>
			<div class="cta-buttons">
				<a href="/contact" class="cta-primary">Book Your Shoot</a>
				<a href="/contact" class="cta-secondary">Get a Quote</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</RootLayout>

